# blog-email

This is a node server that uses REST to create an api to send emails from a blog

## Installation

Use the package manager [pip](https://pip.pypa.io/en/stable/) to install foobar.

```bash
npm install # install packages
```

## Usage
To start the server

```bash
node index.js
```

or run the nodemon server (allows updates without interrupting server)
```bash
nodemon index.js
```

